image_analysis.description: This is an image of page 4 of 51 of an OGE Form 278e, a Public Financial Disclosure Report. The page is titled 'Part 1: Filer's Positions Held Outside United States Government' and lists various organizations associated with the filer, Donald J. Trump. The information is presented in a table format with columns for organization name, location, type, position held, and the start and end dates of the position.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header section with form information and the filer's name. The main body consists of a multi-column table listing positions. A footer contains a note about the data and a document identification number.
